Detailed Description

The class decribes the information of Wifi Protected Setup(WPS)

It setup the pin code and which mode is selected.

 //assume we have a pointer of WpsInfo instance

 //set the pin code
 wps->setPin("1234");

 //set the mode as PBC(Push Button Connection)
 wps->setWpsMode(WpsInfo::WPS_MODE_PBC);

enum gaia::connectivity::WpsInfo::KeyManagement
Enumerator:
KEY_MGMT_PBC 

Push button configuration.

KEY_MGMT_DISPLAY 

Display pin method configuration - pin is generated and displayed on device.

KEY_MGMT_KEYPAD 

Keypad pin method configuration - pin is entered on device.

KEY_MGMT_LABEL 

Label pin method configuration - pin is labelled on device.

KEY_MGMT_INVALID 

Invalid configuration.
